41
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:10,140
She's safe.

42
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:11,600
Don't worry.

43
00:05:12,860 --> 00:05:13,820
Good to know.

44
00:05:17,100 --> 00:05:18,340
For what it's worth,

45
00:05:18,780 --> 00:05:19,660
starting today,

46
00:05:20,140 --> 00:05:21,780
you're my lifesaver.

47
00:05:24,140 --> 00:05:26,100
If you need me
to do anything,

48
00:05:26,380 --> 00:05:27,590
just ask.

49
00:05:28,220 --> 00:05:29,060
Your new life,

50
00:05:29,170 --> 00:05:30,500
I promise you'll have it.

51
00:05:32,780 --> 00:05:34,220
If you're in trouble,

52
00:05:34,950 --> 00:05:36,900
I'll help you
even at the cost of my life.

53
00:05:38,310 --> 00:05:39,150
OK.

54
00:05:40,060 --> 00:05:40,900
Noted.

55
