56
00:05:58,940 --> 00:05:59,780
Oh, actually.

57
00:06:00,540 --> 00:06:02,260
I don't know your name yet.

58
00:06:02,580 --> 00:06:03,420
My prince,

59
00:06:04,700 --> 00:06:05,940
you asked me
to fix my error,

60
00:06:06,100 --> 00:06:07,700
