61
00:06:08,180 --> 00:06:09,100
Guess what?

62
00:06:11,620 --> 00:06:12,620
Prince?

63
00:06:13,700 --> 00:06:14,540
Prince?

64
00:06:16,550 --> 00:06:17,390
Mother,

65
00:06:17,990 --> 00:06:19,260
I have always respected you.

66
00:06:19,940 --> 00:06:21,160
But now I'm in power,

67
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:23,870
it's a felony that you
interfere with my ruling.

68
00:06:25,540 --> 00:06:26,620
Felony?

69
00:06:33,150 --> 00:06:35,140
Emperor, have you forgotten

70
00:06:35,820 --> 00:06:37,310
who led you

71
00:06:37,540 --> 00:06:39,370
to the throne
from the entrance

72
00:06:39,740 --> 00:06:41,390
step by step?

73
00:06:42,790 --> 00:06:44,280
I was young and simple.

74
00:06:45,930 --> 00:06:47,610
I'm grateful
for your instructions.

75
00:06:49,550 --> 00:06:50,640
But now

76
00:06:51,730 --> 00:06:53,330
it's time for you to retire.

77
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:57,440
Putting distant relatives
in important positions

78
00:06:58,850 --> 00:07:00,730
was transgression of power.

79
00:07:01,820 --> 00:07:03,020
- So...
- But don't you worry,

80
00:07:04,140 --> 00:07:06,060
I have that sorted out.

81
00:07:06,700 --> 00:07:08,180
The landscapes are nice
outside the frontier,

82
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:10,140
a much better place

83
