miss the old days

86
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,440
with me in the hall,

87
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,770
you may stay here
for a while longer.

88
00:07:26,140 --> 00:07:26,980
I

89
00:07:27,980 --> 00:07:29,300
shall be off.

90
00:07:35,540 --> 00:07:36,380
You...

