You knew you were lying, huh?

106
00:08:07,060 --> 00:08:08,980
Was it fun to treat me
like a fool?

107
00:08:09,900 --> 00:08:12,180
You enjoyed it when I said
I loved the prince.

108
00:08:12,540 --> 00:08:13,500
